Class FractionTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • tests.FractionTest

  • public class FractionTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Tests the Fraction class. Partitions the input space into the minimum values for numerators and denominators, Integer.MAX_VALUE, numerator greater/less than denominator.
